			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Very nicely described, and exactly correct. I have done this quest, though I had the luxury of doing the quest before they upgraded the two in the tower in Lake Rathe, I soloed both those guy's at 24 before they upgraded them.<BR>
<BR>
Only other comment I would make is that the wand you recieved for the flower that is inside the crypt is used for the Necro Shadow Armor quest. Boot quest I believe, might be gloves though. <BR>
<BR>
This book is alright for a Necromancer. At higher levels it just goes in your bag, and pretty much just pull it out when you want some mana back, but don't want to change into Skeleton form because of factions, such as when your in a city.<BR>
<BR>
Sundahlia &lt;Rise of the Fallen&gt;<BR>
(Rodcet-Nife)
