	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				here is our experience with the quest for words of darkness<BR>
<BR>
it all starts in the temple as you should know by a guy named vulgan i believe.<BR>
<BR>
me and my wife did this quest in two days.<BR>
me 34 paly and her a 34 chanter.<BR>
<BR>
we started in perma. the target is &quot;ICY Goblin&quot; not the common &quot;ICE Goblin&quot;<BR>
<BR>
we grabbed a map to seek out the prison area but there is no real reference to the so called prison area where the icy goblin can be found so ill tell you where it is. there is an halway with 6 round rooms attached to it. i dont recall which room it was it in as we did not see him when we first arrived. so we procedeed to clear out each room 1 by 1 moving to the next room to the right until we got him to spawn. root alot and root often or theese gobbys will run and bring back friends.after operation clean sweep had eliminated all spawns in all of theese rooms we began waiting for the spawns room by room then BOOM! he spawned...we killed.... We Looted the ICY Book ..... we left. got it on the first drop.<BR>
<BR>
next off to lake rathe....we got to the island with the tower on it. there were 3 red conned NPC's outside the tower at great distance. they were amiable to us and out of the range of the tower so we feared them not. we went into the tower and found cynella and her pet next to a wizard NPC named elter or something like that. he conned red to us at 34. this was a delima. if we attacked cynella would the wizard nuke us because he so close to her?...the answer is yes! we both died a miserable death. so went back to recover hour bodies to find them cynella still next to this mean wizard who denies us our book. they were both still amiable even after the combat.so we came up with a plan. i disband from group leaving the wify chanter to watch the action. i attack cynella and run to a point on the island where no npc's are near and chose to die at this location. because i dont want to die in the lake. wify chanter goes to this point of the island and waits for the wizard to leave so she can hail the cynella npc and keep her here. this back fired a lil bit. wizard never left he stayed right there.<BR>
<BR>
finally cynella began to wander about. chanter follows her til she at a safe distance from all four NPC's who are red then hails cynella to hold her there til i get back and loot my corpse. cynella conned light blue to us and her pet was green, so we didnt bother buffing. we just rooted and nuked. she went down easly. we looted....and no book. we then waited for her respawn. which was in the tower. its a ten min respawn. since there was noone in the tower it was safe to kill her there. she spawned and we slayed her before she could summon her pet. she dropped the book of darkness...we left to mistmoore. <BR>
<BR>
mistmoore is an evil and very dangerous place. its a mob zone so i suggest lots of friends to help. we had to invite a druid and a ranger to assist us both 32. we camped the zoneline pulling for about an hour to get the feel for the type of mobs we were dealing with. seemed safe enough. we never died or had to zone . so we decided to go invisible and head towards the graveyard. we went behind the tomb and there was the amible named shadowman. i gave him 2 1hand slash weapons as described. but the shadow only weilded 1 of em. this got me thinking maybe we should only give em 1 at a time. so i gave em another 1 by itself and now he wielded both 1 hand slashes. we slayed him... and he dropped the book. we were so delighted. but this is where it got ugly. our confidence was high and we decided to forgo the invisibilty during to retreat. bad idea. as we walked away 6 targets jumped me. and then another and then another. until there was like i swear...50 or so. i called for an AE mez the chanter complied and boom even more come out...even things i had never seen before showed up...needless to say we all died in the apppropriate setting...a Graveyard. we recovered our corpse later but we still needed to get faction back with the temple so i grabbed the flower(looks like a bag) and gave it to the shadowman we had just slayed. i was invisible so he didnt jump me. we gained faction back for the temple. we waited again like ten miniutes til the flower spwaned again and handed it tot the shadow again just to be sure we would get our faction back. he gives a nec wand only when u do this...not sure about this wand as i destroyed it due to it being nec only and no drop<BR>
someone seek out my revenge for me and kill &quot; the negotiator&quot; she has a real nasty stun spell.<BR>
<BR>
now off to to the temple<BR>
we get there had him the book of shadows. his gives you a note and the list of stuff you need<BR>
<BR>
1.book of darkness<BR>
2.book of frost <BR>
3.return the note<BR>
4.and give him 300 gold pieces<BR>
<BR>
had to run into sol A and buy the gold from another player cause i failed to see this in the subject earlier.<BR>
so we give him everything he asks for<BR>
and we get xp and the book.<BR>
<BR>
book Description<BR>
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP<BR>
+45 Mana<BR>
Effect: Allure of Death<BR>
Class: NEC<BR>
Race: 3 races cant remember them<BR>
<BR>
IT IS NOT FOR CHANTERS<BR>
wish we knew this earlier &lt;sigh&gt;<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Palaneezer and Doneeze Pleezer<BR>
&quot;Friends Upholding Norrath&quot;<BR>
Tarew Marr
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
