	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				*****COMPLETE SPOILER********<BR>
OK, it looks like there are quite a few ideas on this, but I'll tell you that I did this quest with my 30 bard for my necro to attain the words. <BR>
The total time including getting ported by a druid pal was 4 hours, and the lengthiest of it was waiting for the icy gobbie to drop his book.<BR>
 <BR>
First, was in with guild in Perma, we wandered to jail area, the icy gob spawns down in cell every 24 minutes, he dropped the book after killing him the fourth time, you CANNOT solo this area at 30 or lower, you WILL agro down there. Item is no drop. <BR>
<BR>
Next on to Lake Rathe, came out of SK, got loc (come out of zone, swim to left and you will see little island with tower) Upon coming to tower I conned Cyanelle, she was blue to me at 30, and her pet was green. I elected to solo her, and she quickly started wiping my a** all over the place. Couldn't charm pet said &quot;This NPC cannot be charmed&quot; and she was hitting me for over 60 HPs per blow and each cast about 200HPs. I mezzed her and ran to zone. Then incorporating the help of a 41 paladin, we waited three spawns(VERY short spawn rate, 8 minutes) and she dropped the book. She did a number on the pally, and he (seemingly a veteran of the zone) explained that two patches ago they really beefed her up.<BR>
<BR>
On to kill shadowmen. I go to LFay, and get the help of a 50 enchanter. We tried everything with charming, giving weapons, no book dropped. We went to Mistmoor, and behind the crypt is the named shadowman. He is indifferent to us, so we walked over, gave him two one hand slashers, then killed him, easy kill, and he dropped a robe, a gem, and THE BOOK on first kill!!!!!<BR>
<BR>
On to temple,I got the note, switched characters to get necro there with 300 GP. Then handed note back with items to him, camped, back with necro, gave 300 GP...and TADA, my new word of darkness for my little necro  :)<BR>
<BR>
A few things to keep in mind on doing this quest like this folks:<BR>
1) You CANNOT solo that mage in Lake Rathe at 30...she WILL kill you<BR>
2)Your factions with temple get lowered if you kill the named shadowman in Mistmoor (name is Ssynthi? sp)<BR>
3) You should bring a group to Perma for the icy goblin (jail area is down tunnel past scryer spawn, enter first door on right in a big room...platform on left side, walk up and there is a tunnel taking you down to cell area...ALOT of gobbies down there)<BR>
4) I spoke to a 56 wiz who tried helping another necro on this, he told me the icecomet stuff is garbage and doesn't work. Also can tell you that charming to give weapons, or being a skellie is a waste of time...no drops of the book from the shadowmen.<BR>
<BR>
That's the whole spoiler, enjoy your new item should you do this. If not for a certain 41 pally, the enchanter's help...and of course the porter to bring me around...it would've been alot longer.<BR>
<BR>
Tevaryen (Bard) <BR>
Misterm (Necro)<BR>
Beniemen (Ranger)<BR>
all on Cazic Thule server
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
